@startuml
title BP-17 - Bill Assignment to Students

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Choose bill assignment criteria;
if (Assignment is manual?) then (Manual)
  :Select individual students;
else (Bulk)
  :Select class, grade or student group;
endif

:Select payment product and billing period;

|Billing Engine|
:Resolve target student list;
:Validate product and policy;
:Create obligations or skip duplicates according to rule;

if (Assignment completed?) then (Yes)
  :Store created obligation records;
  :Prepare notification event;
else (No)
  :Return assignment error;
  stop
endif

|Parent Guardian|
:Receives new bill visibility;
stop

note right
Current MVP supports assignment through single
and bulk StudentObligation creation endpoints.
end note
@enduml
